metadata.name: DripKids Purple/White 1
metadata.description: DripKids by ThrowdownNFTS.eth is a 1 of 1 splatter paint artwork painted on canvas. The canvas is then photographed, uploaded, and sectioned into nft pieces. Each piece owned will earn you 1 entry into a drawing for a chance to win the real life canvas piece. Drawing will be down once each nft is purchased from that canvas piece. Canvas will be shipped for free.
